Remote
------
1. On disconnection, set all indicators to INACTIVE
2. Mainwindow central widget must be whole screen, not just switches
3. Switches
	- Auto on/off configuration based on time
	- Configure to trip a switch on PIR (see similar function for lamp)
	- Make UI beautiful
4. Weather
	- Temperature icon hue change (green: good, red: warm, blue: cold)
	- Make UI beautiful 
5. PIR
	- Display last n detections
6. Lamp
	- Configure to change hue based on
		- temperature
		- fixed user set color
		- on motion detection with configurable color, duration and clock 
		time(ie, work as motion detector between these times of the day, eg: night lamp)
		- on interaction from remote

